'''{{Path|/etc/portage/categories}}''' is [[Article description::a file that contains a simple list of valid categories that may be used in repositories and the <var>PKGDIR</var> variable.]] The existence of a {{Path|categories}} allows for custom package categories to be created. Custom overlays may define {{Path|profiles/categories}} relative to their overlay root.

== Format ==

* One package category per line.

== Example ==

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/categories|title=Categories file example|1=
app-hackers
media-other
}}

